msgid "Applied. Changes are active for this session."
msgstr "已应用。更改在当前会话中生效。"

msgid "Saved to NsCDE.conf. Changes will persist after restart."
msgstr "已保存到 NsCDE.conf。更改将在重启后保留。"

msgid "Dismiss"
msgstr "关闭"

msgid "Use this dialog to set default applications for common tasks. Select the desired application from each dropdown menu, then click Apply to test or Save to write changes to your NsCDE.conf configuration file."
msgstr "使用此对话框设置常见任务的默认应用程序。从每个下拉菜单中选择所需的应用程序，然后点击[应用]进行测试或点击[保存]将更改写入 NsCDE.conf 配置文件。"
